{"type":"message","id":"bdbde26c","parentId":"f2561c95","timestamp":"2026-03-23T06:32:51.209Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I have the recent news. Let me analyze for importance=2 items. Looking at the data, all items appear to have importance=1. None have importance=2 flagged. But there are some significant market moves:\n\n- 沪指失守3800点，日内跌近4% (importance=1)\n- 深成指跌超4%，全市场近5200只个股下跌 (importance=1)\n- 现货黄金大跌5% (importance=1)\n- COMEX白银期货暴跌10% (importance=1)\n- 纽约期金失守4260美元/盎司 (importance=1)\n\n\n- 广期所钯主力合约暴跌13% 铂主力合约暴跌14% (importance=1)\n- 上期所沪金主力合约大跌8% (importance=1)\n\nI'm noticing these are all marked as importance=1, but the sharp declines in precious metals and the broader market sell-off seem noteworthy. Let me check the database directly to see if there are any importance=2 items I might have missed.","thinkingSignature":"f3490cbc475c0b6061bc3b30d4d18b3ae19d2b246e96bd65fd46f5ce548723b3"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_jd6mjxlro2vi_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/gouzai && python3 -c \"\nimport sqlite3, json\nfrom datetime import datetime, timedelta\n\nconn = sqlite3.connect('news.db')\ncursor = conn.cursor()\n\n# 检查近30分钟 importance=2 的记录\nsince = datetime.utcnow() - timedelta(hours=0.5)\ncursor.execute('''\n    SELECT id, title, source, summary, published_at, importance, category \n    FROM news \n    WHERE importance = 2 \n    ORDER BY fetched_at DESC\n    LIMIT 20\n''')\nprint('=== importance=2 记录 ===')\nfor row in cursor.fetchall():\n    print(row)\n\ncursor.execute('''\n    SELECT COUNT(*) FROM news \n    WHERE fetched_at >= ?\n''', (since.isoformat(),))\nprint(f'近30分钟总记录数: {cursor.fetchone()[0]}')\n\nconn.close()\n\" 2>&1","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":3523,"output":448,"cacheRead":27169,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31140,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total